::Feline::

She felt his strong arms around her.  She kind of liked it actually. 
She pulled away from him only a little bit. Just enough so she could 
look at his face.  She looked into his eyes. "Thank you." She leaned 
foreward and kissed him on the lips.  She purred slightly to enhance 
the kiss.  She pulled back and rubbed her hand up and down his chest.
"I just wanted to thank you properly." she said in a soft voice.  She 
smiled at him.

She shook her head as if to clear it from a spell, "Oh, I'm sorry, I 
guess I kind of...ah..I mean. heh." She looked down and blushed.
